text: Jewel Kilcher (born May 23, 1974), known simply as Jewel, is an American singer-songwriter. She has had four Grammy Award nominations. Jewel was born in Payson, Utah, but raised in Anchorage, Alaska. == References == Category:1974 births Category:Living people Category:American guitarists Category:Musicians from Utah Category:Singers from Utah Category:Singers from Alaska Category:American singer-songwriters Category:Musicians from Anchorage, Alaska
